data.description: Absolutely stunning 3 bed 2 bath + Den + bonus/teen room. Located in Rancho Del Ago and is in  the award winning A+ Vail School District. Too many beautiful upgrades inside and out to list, including Solar, custom barn doors, open-concept kitchen and living space with plenty of room for the whole family.  Beautiful kitchen has an abundance of cabinet and counter space. Gorgeous sparkling pool, private  backyard oasis with no rear neighbors! . Minutes from scenic Del Ago Golf Club, hiking, biking and parks. Colossal Cave is a short drive and is the largest known dry cave in the united states.  You could call this gem, home!
